name: Eel Toss
description:
Eel Toss was a submitted fan-game that was played by the hosts of Fish Center Live (Adult Swim Streams). Long live the streams. 

Choose an eel. Either Promises or Hamburger and take to the field to fly through the water to eat some tasty Crawfish. Be careful to not hit the yellow plastic tank ornaments, Thlump, or bombs.

3D Models, Code, Sound FX are by me. 

Character Portraits and background images are from Fish Center Live.

Fish Center Live is a property of Adult Swim.
